Carl Bradey lost everything he owned in a house fire in Palmerston North last month . 
  The 25-year-old smashed through a window to rescue a three year old girl . 
  He suffered horrific burns to his whole body and nerve damage to his right arm . 
  The fire was started by a candle and destroyed his house and car . 
  He has undergone four major operations since the fire . 
 